              com.microsoft.bingads.bulk.entities.BulkSiteLink

public class BulkSiteLink
extends SingleRecordBulkEntity

Represents a subset of the fields in a Sitelink Ad Extension record. The Sitelink Ad Extension record includes the distinct properties of the BulkSiteLink class, combined with the commmon properties of the BulkSiteLinkAdExtension class, for example BulkAccount and SiteLinksAdExtension"/>. For more information, see Sitelink Ad Extension at http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkID=511517.
